{"tid":780173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★2018年8月15 有調查指基金經理看好科技股","createTime":"2018-08-15T03:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T11:13:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"35f24cf5ee1d3bd862e6746a4aaa8d807bc49dc9","tid":780173,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:34:38.000Z","msg":"有調查顯示，基金經理最看好中美科技股，和沽售新興市場股票。  土耳其貨幣危機引發新興市場震盪，但原來在上周五爆發前，大型投資者可能已看淡。  美銀美林上周調查逾240名基金經理，沽新興市場股票成為第二受歡迎的交易，但平均持倉僅較基準指數低百分之1，較上次新興市場危機時，低百分之27少，相信再減持空間仍很大。  至於最受歡迎的交易，連續七個月都是中國和美國的主要科技股，例如騰訊、阿里巴巴、百度、蘋果公司、亞馬遜等。  最看好的市場，五年來首次是美股，平均持倉較基準指數高一成九，比例是超過三年半以來最高，較上月亦大升10個百分點。  主要原因是公司盈利，六成七受訪者同意美國企業盈利較強，比例是17年來最高。而且聯儲局漸進加息，資金環境仍然充裕，都利好美股。  但美銀美林本身不同意，認為企業債務高，債券息率回報較股票吸引，而且盈利前景有轉弱風險，有利防守性股票。  部分基金經理態度亦較審慎，平均持有現金比例，升0.3個百分點至百分之5；約五成七受訪者亦表明，美國關稅引發貿易糾紛升溫，是全球經濟最大風險。  在土耳其危機爆發後，投資者看法亦更審慎。  摩根大通周一做調查發現，傳統避險資產之一，長期美國國債的投資者，持有淡倉或減持的比例，由三成四降至三成。持倉沒有變化的投資者，由五成一升至五成七。看好的投資者比例，由一成半降至一成三。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/113435_add83aefb67ac08f3273b3017431bf6a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F113435_add83aefb67ac08f3273b3017431bf6a.png&h=a31e6e36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/finance/5b737759e60383e457f5f4c1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Ffinance%2F5b737759e60383e457f5f4c1%2F&d=nOKVOrQ%2BeJKlB8hxaAzPobIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=5531f01c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/finance/5b737759e60383e457f5f4c1/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea9f53aadf48df7521fc4700502f10e5326410c","tid":780173,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:34:52.000Z","msg":"走鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e57a456edd73519ef8e289387745ecacb2e545","tid":780173,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/15/113625_66a38d5983debc33002441664f91dab4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F15%2F113625_66a38d5983debc33002441664f91dab4.png&h=8997fcb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cf706f2024e76d4d7992683ea177ef5d4f48366","tid":780173,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:43:00.000Z","msg":"美國科技股就美國科技股啦 係都要夾硬加中國落去"},{"pid":"befa7a713ac9cfef16212c8457b6fbd45d3fd4e4","tid":780173,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cf706f2024e76d4d7992683ea177ef5d4f48366","tid":780173,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:43:00.000Z","msg":"美國科技股就美國科技股啦 係都要夾硬加中國落去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:43:30.000Z","msg":"有影700"},{"pid":"b7466ca42dc71b1f663032a29779e5657e7a0fa0","tid":780173,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:44:00.000Z","msg":"佢唔話睇好，班傻散點會衝入去買，冇人買佢點走貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c83a01f540d523c5039c9c3ab10b6a47d8be303","tid":780173,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cf706f2024e76d4d7992683ea177ef5d4f48366","tid":780173,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:43:00.000Z","msg":"美國科技股就美國科技股啦 係都要夾硬加中國落去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:44:22.000Z","msg":"Cctvb嘛"},{"pid":"a547533138362ba61b52fb08d125c2b67732f59e","tid":780173,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:44:47.000Z","msg":"結論：IT=發達"},{"pid":"9d1b45207b50f3c5e353a91c59a0e60a9494b71f","tid":78017